basic.Peptide Name: ToAP3 (scorpions, arachnids, Chelicerata, arthropods, invertebrates, animals)
basic.Target Organism: Active against C. albicans SC5314 (MIC 25 uM), C. tropicalis ATCC 750 (MIC 12.5 uM), C. parapsilosis ATCC 22019 (MIC 100 uM), C. neoformans H99 serotype A (MIC 100 uM), and C. neoformans B3501 serotype D (MIC 25 uM).
